|WKBMetaphysician Help
------------------|YKO

The Metaphysician has entered our world to help adventurers increase
their physical and mental beings. For a cost, he can help you raise
your CON, STR, INT, DEX, WIS, CHR, HP, or SP. The higher your stats
become, the harder it is for him to help you, and the higher the
cost becomes.

At this time, the primary stats of CON, STR, INT, DEX, WIS, and
CHR can only be increased a total of 100; 1 per 'meta'. HPs and SPs
have no such restriction, but only increase between 2 and 7 each 'meta'.

The Metaphysician will only help those that have reached the maximum
level of 250, as his time and energies are costly.
